title: DeepSeek And Its Applications in Biomedical Research
description: By deploying the deepseek R1 model to the server and fine tune with biomedical data on downstream tasks, we are now able to utilize it better in the feild of bioinfomatics.

title: Tesla Stock Price Prediction with Q-Learning.
description: By deploying a classic probalistic learning approach, we get to explore how this can be effective in stock markets.

title: Bank Marketing
description: A Naive Bayes Model is trained to evaluate the risk of lending to specific clients

title: ViT or CNN? A Comparative Study of Image Classification Models via chest X-ray
description: By training series of ViT (Visual Transformers) and CNN on the latest public chest X-ray dataset released by Emory University, we get to evaluate the performances in biomedical studies
